title: Sultan disapproves hearses being used for protest
text:
More 
Selangor ruler Sultan Sharifuddin Idris Shah has expressed his disapproval over the misuse of hearses managed by mosque committees in the state. 
Though there was no mention of names or specific incidents, it wan an obvious response to the protest held outside the state secretariat building in Shah Alam on Feb 14 by Sungai Besar Umno division chief Jamal Md Yunos.
